com.alexgilleran.icesoap.soapfault
Class SOAP11Fault

java.lang.Object
  com.alexgilleran.icesoap.soapfault.SOAP11Fault

public class SOAP11Fault
extends Object

Represents consistent elements of a SOAP 1.1 Fault. Note that the contents of the <detail> tag depends on the service being consumed - to parse this, extend this class.

Author:
Alex Gilleran
